  "2181950": {
    "name": "零异机动队",
    "steam_appid": 2181950,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎加入我们的游戏讨论群</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方玩家群：548253790<br><strong>如加群时提示群已满，欢迎加入2群 ：996760787</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们期望听到你的声音! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到余烬之城</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >泽祖拉从前是一座繁盛的庞大都市，在一场旷日持久的世界大战中几近全毁--这是一场滥用AGI（人工通用智能）引发的恶果。泽祖拉被认为是仅存的AGI数据中心所在地，城市的周围由各托拉斯围建起禁区。对外宣传是为了保护公众不受失控的AGI衍生影响，但实际上只是确保能控制泽祖拉的科技遗产。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/b2e414bb8396279a987e09b1a19551a4.poster.avif?t=1748518353\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/b2e414bb8396279a987e09b1a19551a4.webm?t=1748518353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/b2e414bb8396279a987e09b1a19551a4.mp4?t=1748518353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 游戏玩法——三人小队，三套牌组，穷尽算力展开精妙配合</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/924b9251a1eff4846673d2f79f313b6a.poster.avif?t=1748518353\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/924b9251a1eff4846673d2f79f313b6a.webm?t=1748518353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/924b9251a1eff4846673d2f79f313b6a.mp4?t=1748518353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在泽祖拉禁区，没人可以单打独斗做到“大名鼎鼎”，你需要在三个核心职业共计九名专家中，选择出一个三人小队。你可以选择老派战术，或者以极端的搭配扭曲常规，只要你自信有足够的技巧引导他们冲破泽城禁区，任何疯狂的想法都是可行的。这里没有真正的主角，每个“无名之辈”都同等重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 使用CCG风格的牌组战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/ada7c3315132904cab3143900f5b4183.poster.avif?t=1748518353\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/ada7c3315132904cab3143900f5b4183.webm?t=1748518353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/ada7c3315132904cab3143900f5b4183.mp4?t=1748518353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色都配有单独的牌组，其中至少包含8张角色专属牌和至少12张自组卡牌。反抗军们习惯武装到牙齿——牌组不能少于20张，暴露任何短板都意味着死亡。为了确保成功，要充分利用牌组之间的协同作用，并变化策略来击败敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 多阶段Boss战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/3fe7db1916249758d0799b706b13cd24.poster.avif?t=1748518353\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/3fe7db1916249758d0799b706b13cd24.webm?t=1748518353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/3fe7db1916249758d0799b706b13cd24.mp4?t=1748518353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含受MMO团本启发的多阶段Boss战，每场Boss战都有令人眼前一亮的新机制和特殊能力。挑战庞大战争机器—破城者；击败骇人听闻的试验品-密特兰公牛；亦或是在炮艇的火力倾泻下保卫穹顶。战胜超过12名强大的首领，带给你分量十足的战斗快感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战役模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/72c67ea2620acd9bc1cd9d2a18a5ea16.poster.avif?t=1748518353\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/72c67ea2620acd9bc1cd9d2a18a5ea16.webm?t=1748518353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/72c67ea2620acd9bc1cd9d2a18a5ea16.mp4?t=1748518353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每轮剧情模式游戏中，在抵达禁区的黑暗中心之前，你可以自由选择穿过6个城区中的3个。每场旅程都将改变你的团队，用极具侵略性的植入体抑或是不计后果的生化药剂对成员加以改造。你可以选择成为一位开明的导师，让队员变为坚不可摧的战士；或者成为一个赛博疯子，让队员仅作为携带AGI病毒的载体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>现开模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/8ab66495a254e26b5232955b0c0578d9.poster.avif?t=1748518353\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/8ab66495a254e26b5232955b0c0578d9.webm?t=1748518353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181950/extras/8ab66495a254e26b5232955b0c0578d9.mp4?t=1748518353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除剧情模式外，我们还为挑战者准备了现开模式。在该模式下，每轮游戏开始前你将直接获得大量卡包，挑选其中的卡牌从零构筑你的牌组，对抗随机且逐渐升级的艰难Boss连战。在面对泽祖拉中最危险的敌人之前，你能走多远？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>局外收集</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小队将在战斗中获得“合成记忆”，通过Failsafe系统使用这些合成记忆将战斗中获得的强力卡牌永久地加入到你的收藏中。加入收藏后的卡牌可以带入下轮战役中，极大增强卡组构筑稳定性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
